		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's probably the golden point for bankswitching, somewhere between cycles 256~323. AFAIK, it never access $2007, as mentioned "there and there". <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br /><strong>Update:</strong> the game does NOT glitch if a tile fetch occurs on dot 256 (257th pixel). Works fine. The game fetches tiles $FD-&gt;$FE-&gt;$FD-&gt;$FE-&gt;... and if the fetch at 256 isn't allowed, it glitches.

		

