		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The fetch should occur after the 8th and final pixel of the FD/FE tile is drawn. It's pretty straight forward in that respect. But I am not sure how you render graphics. Someway you need to implement so that after the tile pattern fetch for the 8 pixels of tile FD/FE for it to trigger the bankswitching. Switching apon reads through $2007 is not important to get PunchOut working properly as I remember.

		

		</td>
