	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I fixed the sprites by doing CHR bankswitches during cycles 256~320 of sprite fetches. Since the game uses 8x8 sprites, you should check the secondary OAM, the tile number stored there.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


